<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186289>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 10. Details of males of Munina. 5 – 6: aedeagus (dorsal view at left, lateral view at right); 7 – 8: pronotum; 9 – 10: last ventrite. 5, 7, 9 — M. donacioides; 6, 8, 10 — M. laotica sp. nov. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186289/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

